2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel method that combines learning with post-processing update steps to adapt to a fast approximation model. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper involves the use of neural networks for style transfer. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with generating artistic effects on images. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper involves the transfer of artistic styles to images, which is a multimedia application.
